query:
INSERT INTO task(
                task_id,
                queue_name,
                status,
                parent_task_id,
                idempotency_key,
                project_id,
                schedule)
        VALUES ($1, $2, 'enabled', $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_idempotency_key DO NOTHING
        RETURNING task_id
